title: Taqyeem - Premium WordPress Review Plugin
description:
Taqyeem is a premium reviewing and rating WordPress plugin. This plugin was built for adding lovely ratings and reviews to your posts, pages, and custom post types. Use the customization options to create the perfect ratings addition to your website. Change the fonts, image, colors, style, and of course the criteria. 

Taqyeem WordPress Review Plugin Features
Unlimited colors 
Unlimited Review Criterias 
Supports post , pages and custom post types 
Typography Options 
500+ Google Web Fonts. (Change elements fonts in the theme settings) 
RTL Support 
Schema SEO Rich Snippet Review Microdata 
Allow users to rate 
Best, Recent & rand. reviews widget 
3 Review Styles : Stars, Points & percentage 
Multiple options for the rate image 

This plugin has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress plugin. 

Product page: http://codecanyon.net/item/taqyeem-wordpress-review-plugin/4558799
